# NST-FRC32 Licensing

This repository uses a dual-license model to protect both open hardware designs and software source code.

---

## Hardware License

All files within the `/hardware` directory (including schematics, PCB manufacturing files, BOM, CPL, and 3D models) are licensed under the **CERN Open Hardware Licence Version 2 - Strongly Reciprocal (CERN-OHL-S-2.0)**.

Under this license:
* You are free to manufacture, modify, and distribute these hardware designs.
* Any modifications or derivative hardware designs must be published under the same CERN-OHL-S-2.0 license.
* Attribution to the original author (**Hugo Llanos - Nostec**) must be maintained in all documentation and physical board markings.

Full license text: https://ohwr.org/cern_ohl_s_v2.txt

---

## Firmware License

All source code and firmware files within the `/firmware` directory are licensed under the **GNU General Public License v3.0 (GPLv3)**.

Under this license:
* You are free to run, study, modify, and share the software.
* Any modified version of the software must also be distributed under the GPLv3 license.
* Attribution to the original author (**Hugo Llanos - Nostec**) must be maintained.

Full license text: https://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl-3.0.txt

